title: Playin Blitz, my Cait's pretty much useless
body:
Instead of just giving up on the lane and playing super passive until team phase (like I would with other supports), I decided to casually go mid and get Kat ten fuckin kills. 
Cait, on the other hand constantly complained about me "KSing all the time" 
I was 5/6/19
Kat was 18/1
Cait was 5/5 (from using q and ult on things Kat didn't instakill :^)
